data_table.description: Sample - Attribute information includes data of n=20 Eigenvectors.

variable.name: C1
variable.comment: Eigenvectors from principal components analyses to approximate popualtion substructure based on high quality common polymophisms (minor allele frequency > 0.05) and not in linkage with any proximal variants (no SNPs with r2 > 0.5 within 250kb).
